        <item>
            <title>【教學】泰國一鍵報警 App 註冊，支援香港電話、一鍵即分享位置</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/05/thailand-tourist/life-tech/travel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=thailand-tourist</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/05/thailand-tourist/life-tech/travel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 05 Feb 2025 10:43:07 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[旅遊]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Thailand Tourist Police]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[泰國]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290047</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>泰國近日傳出擄劫遊客至「KK 園區」消息，令旅客人心惶惶。為保障遊客，泰國警方推出了官方手機報警 App「Thailand Tourist Police」，遊客能夠利用這個 App 一鍵報警，並將位置分享予泰國警方。應用程式支援中文，同時可分享相片予泰國警方尋求協助。如果你最近會去泰國，就一定要預先下載這個 App 了。</p><h2>Step 1 下載 Thailand Tourist Police</h2><p>使用手機在 App Store / Google Play Store 下載「Thailand Tourist Police」APP。</p><p>下載連結：</p><p>Apple App Store：<a href="https://apps.apple.com/app/thailand-tourist-police">https://apps.apple.com/app/thailand-tourist-police</a></p><p>Google Play：<a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=tourist.police.app">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=tourist.police.app</a></p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290058" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1348-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1348-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1348.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲下載 「Thailand Tourist Police」</p><h2>Step 2 註冊帳户</h2><p>開啟應用程式後，可見「Thailand Tourist Police」支援多國語言，你可以選擇中文（簡體）。選擇中文後點擊 Select。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290059" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_1.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲選擇中文後點擊 Select</p><p>現在你會看見註冊畫面，你可選擇使用電郵註冊，也可連結 Google / Apple 帳户。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290060" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1351-1-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1351-1-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1351-1.jpg 415w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可選擇使用電郵註冊，或者也可以使用 Google / Apple 帳户</p><p>小編選擇使用 Apple 帳户建立 Thailand Tourist Police 帳户，那就無須輸入電郵地址。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290061" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_2-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_2-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_2.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可直接連結你的 Apple 帳户</p><p>輸入電話號碼，接下來你可以點擊下一步。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290062" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_3-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_3-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_3.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲輸入電話號碼</p><p>接下來你需要填寫個人資料，填寫好之後可以點擊下一步。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290063" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1358-268x580.jpg" alt="" width="268" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1358-268x580.jpg 268w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/img_1358.jpg 415w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 268px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲填好個人資料就可寫「下一步」</p><p>閲讀條款後滑動到最抵，點擊「接受」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290069" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_4-535x580.jpg" alt="" width="535" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_4-535x580.jpg 535w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/tp_4.jpg 830w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 535px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲點擊「接受」</p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
